"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-most-iconic-moments-best-photographs-paris-olympics-b1175605.html\", \"text\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies. Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search. See our privacy policy for more information.  Sport|Olympics  As the2024 Summer Olympic Gamesare coming to an end, photographers have worked tirelessly to capture the most iconic moments throughout the event.  From North and South Korean athletes posing up for a selfie together after their table tennis showdown-toTeam GB's Tom Daleygetting a victory kiss from Noah Williamson-to the photograph dubbed as the most iconic of the Summer Olympics-to Diana, the widow of the late Olympic weightlifter Oleksandr Pielieshenko, who was killed fighting against Russia's invasion, the multi-sport event has created many happy and sad moments.  The Evening Standard has compiled twenty best photographs from the 2024Paris Olympics:  Paris 2024: Tom Daley delivers super silver with Noah Williams after delaying Olympic farewell  Team GB reach 50-medal mark at Paris Olympics as Ellie Aldridge delivers 13th gold in kitesurfing  Italian boxer 'never felt punch like this' as she quit Olympic bout against athlete who failed 'gender test'  Today's Olympics schedule: Team GB events, Day 14 medal highlights and how to watch the Paris Games  This selection of pictures is edited by the Evening Standard's picture editorsElliot WaglandandDebasish Sarmah.  MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\"}"